high_descs: Turn around and head to the kitchen on the left and face the cutting board on the right.
Pick up the mango from the cutting board.
Turn right to face the sink.
Wash the mango in the sink and take it out.
Turn around to head to the fridge.
Put the mango in the bottom shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed Mango in the Fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, walk straight towards a wall to your left, turn left after passing the wall, and walk to the countertop.
Pick up a mango on a stick from a cutting board next to a kitchen sink.
Take a step closer to the sink.
Put the mango on a stick in the sink, rinse it with water, and take it out.
Turn around and head to the fridge to your right.
Put the mango on a stick in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Get the rinsed Mango on a stick in the fridge

high_descs: Take the fruit in the counter top
Put the fruit in the sink, clean it off
Place the fruit on the fridge
